      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 39,
      "message": "I think it may be better to add it under <dependencyManagement> as a <dependency>. In that case the child pom's only need to mention the dependency name and not refer the version attribute at all.\n\nExample (in child pom) -\n\n<dependency>\n    <groupId>commons-cli</groupId>\n    <artifactId>commons-cli</artifactId>\n</dependency>",
